    Class Description
    Docker
    This class abstracts client access to the Docker API through DockerClient.
    Docker.Bindings
    This class represents a list of bindings for volumes on the docker container and host machine.
    Docker.Command
    This class represents a command that can be executed on the container
    Docker.Shell
    This enum represents shells that the Docker class supports
    DockerException
    This class provides an exception for anything that may occur in the package
    DockerSandbox
    This class provides an "API" to abstract the classes of this module into an easy to use interface to allow commands to be run in sandboxed docker containers.
    Profile
    This class represents an execution profile for a docker container to be spun up from.
    Profile.Limits
    This class represents limits that a created docker container must adhere to
    Result
    This class represents the result of a docker execution.
    Utils
    This class provides utilities for the library
    WorkingDirectory
    The WorkingDirectory class provides an abstraction surrounding the passing of files between the host machine and the docker container.
    WorkingDirectory.UploadedFile
    This class represents a file that will be uploaded to the working directory
